  description="Brian McMahon founded Nous Ergon, an applied AI lab, in March 2026. His two decades of experience intersect tech and finance — a decade in data science and machine learning, a decade in investment banking and advisory."
>
  <section class="max-w-3xl mx-auto px-6 pt-16 pb-12">
    <h1 class="text-2xl md:text-3xl font-semibold text-zinc-100 mb-2">Brian McMahon</h1>
    <p class="text-sm text-zinc-500 mb-8">Founder</p>

